"localparam LATENCY    = bram_dual_port_simple_LATENCY   (REGISTERED_IN)"
- defined as 
"bram_single_port_LATENCY(REGISTERED_IN);"
- defined as 
"
int latency = 1;
if(REGISTERED_IN == 1) latency = 2;
return latency;
"
- which is correct, the latency is 1, and increases to 2 if REGISTERED_IN == 1
